[[Image:TurinPapyrus1.jpg|thumb]]描繪在Wadi Hammamat裡金礦的位置，被認為是最古老的地圖]]
'''[[埃及|埃及]]的[[採礦業|採礦業]]'''歷史非常悠久。埃及擁有大量的礦產資源，其中包括4800萬噸的[[鉭|鉭]]（世界第4多）、5000萬噸的[[煤|煤]]和[[東部沙漠|東部沙漠]]下670萬盎司的[[金|金]]<ref name=MPR>{{cite web |title=Mining in Egypt – Unexplored Territory |url=http://www.gcgf.org/ifcext/mena.nsf/AttachmentsByTitle/Miningpolicyreformegypt/$FILE/Egypt+Mining+Brochure+English.pdf |publisher=International Finance Corporation |accessdate=2008-03-22 |format=PDF |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110201103515/http://www.gcgf.org/ifcext/mena.nsf/AttachmentsByTitle/Miningpolicyreformegypt/%24FILE/Egypt%2BMining%2BBrochure%2BEnglish.pdf |archivedate=2011-02-01 }}</ref>，部分地區還有[[油田|油田]]。這些礦產資源價值總和在1986年時約[[埃及鎊|£E]]1.02億元（1870萬美元），與1981年的£E6000萬（1100美元）相差甚遠<ref name=LOC>{{cite web | url = http://lcweb2.loc.gov/frd/cs/egtoc.html | title = A Country Study: Egypt | publisher = US [[Library_of_Congress|Library of Congress]], [[Federal_Research_Division|Federal Research Division]] | date = December 1993 | accessdate = 2008-03-22 | archive-date = 2015-07-20 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150720233852/http://lcweb2.loc.gov/frd/cs/egtoc.html | dead-url = no }} ''This article incorporates text from the source, which is in the [[public_domain|public domain]].''</ref>。主要出口的礦物為[[鐵礦石|鐵礦石]]、[[磷酸鹽|磷酸鹽]]和[[鹽|鹽]]，根據1986年的資料，三者生產總值分別為2,048、1,310及1,233噸，與1981年的2,139、691及883噸有明顯的變化。此外，少量的[[石棉|石棉]]（313噸）和[[石英|石英]]（19噸）資源於1986年正式開採<ref name=LOC/>，而[[西奈半島|西奈半島]]則被認為沉積著[[鋅|鋅]]、[[錫|錫]]、[[鉛|鉛]]與[[銅|銅]]<ref name=LOC/>。私人企業的探索和開採活動通常是有限的<ref name=MPR/>，但2009年，總部設在澳大利亞的[[Centamin_Egypt有限公司|Centamin Egypt礦產探勘有限公司]]對金礦[[歐蘇克|歐蘇克]]（Alsukari）進行大規模開採<ref name=tele>[http://www.telegraph.co.uk/finance/markets/questor/5120791/Centamin-Egypt-on-track-for-imminent-production.html Centamin Egypt on track for imminent production] {{Wayback|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/finance/markets/questor/5120791/Centamin-Egypt-on-track-for-imminent-production.html |date=20170909165541 }} Daily Telegraph, 7 April 2009</ref>，且有不錯的收穫<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mining-journal.com/production-and-markets/centamin-maintains-2011-production-guidance|accessdate=2011-04-11|title=Mining Journal - Centamin maintains 2011 production guidance|date=2011-04-11|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120318035039/http://www.mining-journal.com/production-and-markets/centamin-maintains-2011-production-guidance|archivedate=2012-03-18}}</ref>。
